      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This car is full of personality and waiting for someone who can give it a little extra love! While it has seen plenty of adventures and shows significant wear both inside and out, it\u2019s a great opportunity for a mechanic or DIY enthusiast to bring it back to its best. It's an honest, high-mileage vehicle with a lot of stories to tell!",
