    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition, ideal for someone looking for a reliable and well-maintained daily driver. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, showing the care it has received over the years. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age. All essential features are fully functional, providing a comfortable and confident driving experience for its next owner.",
