    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It runs like an absolute dream and has been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This example is mechanically pristine, delivering razor-sharp throttle response through its individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and professional rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, preserving the chassis's renowned communicative feedback. A turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service records. No accidents. Flawless interior and exterior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
