    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and feels as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the depth and luster of its original factory paint, which remains free of any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of any creases or wear marks, and still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. We have a comprehensive binder of every service performed at the authorized dealership, including a recent preventative fluid overhaul. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
